      "value": "<p>&gt;@Compendium[sfrpg.class-features.PU3uwrAcmGXMGo2n]{Specialization}</p>\n<p><span id=\"ctl00_MainContent_DataListTalentsAll_ctl04_LabelName\">You can move from place to place without being noticed.<br /><br /><strong>Associated Skills</strong>: Engineering and Sleight of Hand. You can attempt an Engineering check with a +4 bonus to make a trick attack by using a customized device to momentarily distract your enemy.<br /><strong>Specialization Exploit</strong>: @Compendium[sfrpg.class-features.583I8ujhHputWnep]{Utility Belt (Ex)}<br /><strong>Quick Deployment (Ex)</strong>: At 11th level, once per round you can retrieve or put away a stored item (including from your utility belt) or pick up an item as part of another move action, standard action, or full action.</span></p>",
